div.div:
All states =
IDLE,
SERVE_IR, DONE_IR,
SERVE_DR, DONE_DR,
SERVE_DW, DONE_DW
Start at IDLE
IDLE:
if (i_read) Move to SERVE_IR
elif (d_read) Move to SERVE_DR
elif (d_write) Move to SERVE_DW
SERVE_IR:
p_addr = i_addr
p_read = 1
if (p_resp) Move to DONE_IR
DONE_IR:
i_rdata = p_rdata
i_resp = 1
Move to IDLE
SERVE_DR:
p_addr = d_addr
p_read = 1
if (p_resp) Move to DONE_DR
DONE_DR:
d_rdata = p_rdata
d_resp = 1
Move to IDLE
SERVE_DW:
p_addr = d_addr
p_wdata = d_wdata
p_write = 1
if (p_resp) Move to DONE_DW
DONE_DW:
d_resp = 1
Move to IDLE
